divs: Sighting Details1. I was drivin through Virginia and I took a picture of the sky and it was clear with nothing in the sky and then looked at the picture and there was a UFO looking Object in the picture but not in the sky. 2. Looking at the picture.
Summary: I was driving through Virginia heading home from North Carolina I looked at the sky and there was nothing I then took a picture of the sky and then looked back at the sky it wasn't there then looked at the picture and saw that light but not in the sky
